---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base title="Sectors — PerfEco Consulting" description="PerfEco works in industry, energy, construction, banking and the public sector across New Caledonia and French Polynesia.">
  <Nav />
  <main class="pt-16">

    <section class="bg-navy-dark text-white py-20 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-teal font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Sectors</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Complex environments, an adapted method</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg">Subsidiaries of international groups, multi-entity structures, local regulatory constraints — PerfEco knows these environments from the inside.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-4">⚡</div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-1">Industry &amp; Energy</h2>
            <p class="text-teal text-xs font-medium mb-4">ENGIE, Vale, Prony Resources, TotalEnergies, Enercal</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5">Environments under regulatory and technical pressure. Multi-level reporting, IT governance and complex industrial project management.</p>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-teal rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Reliable production reporting</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-teal rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Multi-entity management</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-teal rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Regulatory compliance</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-teal rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Organisational transformation</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🏗️</div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-1">Construction &amp; Maintenance</h2>
            <p class="text-teal text-xs font-medium mb-4">Dumez, VCOM, multi-entity groups</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5">Groups in transformation requiring solid structuring and pragmatic digitalisation of operational processes.</p>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-teal rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Multi-entity structuring</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-teal rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Project tracking</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-teal rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Tool adoption</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-teal rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Cross-team coordination</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🏦</div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-1">Banking &amp; Insurance</h2>
            <p class="text-teal text-xs font-medium mb-4">Pacific financial institutions</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5">Local and regional regulatory constraints. Need for reliable reporting, compliance and risk management.</p>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-teal rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Risk management</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-teal rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Regulatory reporting</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-teal rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Process simplification</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-teal rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Data governance</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🏛️</div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-1">Public &amp; Parapublic sector</h2>
            <p class="text-teal text-xs font-medium mb-4">Province Sud, OPT, CCI, CAFAT, CHT Médipôle, CHS</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5">Public bodies and institutions in NC &amp; PF facing increasing budget pressure and modernisation needs.</p>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-teal rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Budget optimisation</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-teal rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Service digitalisation</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-teal rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Team performance</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-teal rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Reporting to supervisory bodies</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-14 bg-navy-dark text-white rounded-2xl p-10 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Your sector is not listed?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">PerfEco works in any complex organisational environment. The method adapts — the results remain measurable.</p>
          <a href="/en/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-teal hover:bg-teal-dark text-white font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors">
            Discuss your context
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>
